Class PetList

java.lang.Object
model.PetList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class PetList extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a list of pets. Provides methods to add, edit, remove, and retrieve pets. This class implements Serializable to allow instances to be serialized.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Piotr Junosz
